<%
    getTag = function(item){
      var skills = cv.skills;
      skills.find(x=>x.items)
    }
%>
<div class="flex flex-row flex-wrap-reverse w-full justify-around">
    <div class="w-full md:w-1/3 md:p-2 print-preview-full">
        <h3>Languages:</h3>
        <ul class="text-gray-900 mt-8 print:mt-0">
            <%for (language of cv.languages) {%>
            <li>
                <div class="flex flex-row flex-wrap items-center mt-2 mr-4 print:mt-0">
                    <div class="w-full">
                        <%=language.name%>
                    </div>
                    <div class="w-full">
                        <div class="w-full bg-transparent">
                            <div class="print-preview-lanuage-bar
                                        bg-yellow-500
                                        font-semibold
                                        text-gray-700
                                        flex
                                        align-center
                                        justify-center
                                        text-center
                                        p-0.5
                                        leading-none
                                        rounded-full" style="width: <%=language.percentage%>%">
                                <%=language.level%>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </li>
            <%}%>
        </ul>
        <h3 class="pt-3">
            Awards:
        </h3>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-end mr-4">
        <span class="rounded-full
            text-gray-500
            bg-gray-200
            font-semibold
            border
            border-solid
            border-gray-300
            flex
            align-center
            transition
            duration-300
            ease w-max align-middle">
                <img class="rounded-full w-9 h-9 max-w-none print-preview-hide" alt="A"
                     src="/assets/icons/oitm.png" />
                <span class="flex items-center px-3 py-1 flex-wrap">
                  V. Országos IT Megmérettetés - Angular I. place
                </span>
          </span>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="w-full md:w-2/3 pr-4 pt-0 print-preview-full ">
        <h2>Expertise</h2>
        <p class="text-justify mt-8">
            During my years in the software industry, I worked with numerous technologies. The below-listed ones are that I currently use  on a daily basis. I believe the most important is to choose the right technology and the right approach for every task, individually.
        </p>
        <ul class="mt-1">
        <%for(skill of cv.skills) {%>
            <li class="mb-1">
                <p class="font-bold">
                    <%=skill.name%>
                </p>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-around print:hidden">
                    <%for(item of skill.items){%>
                  <span class="rounded-full
                  <%=item.text || (item.color ? 'text-gray-100' : 'text-gray-600')%>
                  font-semibold
                  border
                  border-solid
                  border-gray-300
                  flex
                  align-center
                  transition
                  duration-300
                  ease
                  mt-2
                  mx-2
                  w-max" style="background-color: <%=item.color%>; -webkit-print-color-adjust: economy">
                    <img class="rounded-full w-9 h-9 max-w-none print-preview-hide" alt="A"
                         src="<%=item.icon%>" />
                    <span class="flex items-center px-3 py-2 print-preview-chip">
                      <%=item.name%>
                    </span>
